OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1776442271
OL,3,CPolice officer committed gross
OL,4,Cmisconduct for pursuing relationship
OL,5,Cwith woman
OL,7,FA Warwickshire Police detective who
OL,8,Fpursued a romantic relationship the
OL,9,Fmother of a child victim has been
OL,10,Ffound to have committed gross
OL,11,Fmisconduct following an investigation
OL,12,Fby the Independent Office for Police
OL,13,FConduct (IOPC).
OL,15,FDC John Littlewood, 52, admitted one
OL,16,Fcount of improper exercise of police
OL,17,Fpowers and privileges by a constable
OL,18,Fat court hearing in January.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/7
