PN,37302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1776442271
OL,3,CPolice officer committed gross
OL,4,Cmisconduct for pursuing relationship
OL,5,Cwith woman
OL,7,FHe exchanged more than 300 messages,
OL,8,Fmany of which were sexualised, with a
OL,9,Fwoman he met while investigating a
OL,10,Freport of a sexual assault against the
OL,11,Fwoman's daughter in October 2021.
OL,13,FOne message from Littlewood read: "if
OL,14,Fyou are careless with my messages and
OL,15,Fdon't delete them you could really
OL,16,Fdrop me in it at work".
OL,26,@uD@cOUxD@VO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
