OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1776442271
OL,3,CPolice officer committed gross
OL,4,Cmisconduct for pursuing relationship
OL,5,Cwith woman
OL,7,FThe IOPC investigation found
OL,8,FLittlewood frequently visited the
OL,9,Fwoman's home and met her at a Coventry
OL,10,Fhotel in the early hours of 1 October
OL,11,F2023 for around 50 minutes.
OL,13,FHe was given an eight-month prison
OL,14,Fsentence, suspended for 15 months, and
OL,15,Fordered to carry out 100 hours of work
OL,16,Fin the community.
OL,18,FHe had worked in the force's Child
OL,19,FAbuse, Trafficking and Exploitation
OL,20,Fteam but left the force before the
OL,21,Finvestigation began in December 2023.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
