OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1776442271
OL,3,CPolice officer committed gross
OL,4,Cmisconduct for pursuing relationship
OL,5,Cwith woman
OL,7,FA misconduct hearing today concluded
OL,8,FLittlewood would have been dismissed
OL,9,Fwith immediate effect.
OL,11,FHe will now be placed on the barred
OL,12,Flist and won't be able to work in
OL,13,Fpolicing again.
OL,15,FIOPC Director Derrick Campbell, said:
OL,16,F"DC Littlewood was working in the
OL,17,Fpublic protection unit at the time of
OL,18,Fthese allegations and, as such, had
OL,19,Faccess to vulnerable women. He held a
OL,20,Fposition of trust.
OL,26,@xD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/7
