FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1776442271
OL,3,CPolice officer committed gross
OL,4,Cmisconduct for pursuing relationship
OL,5,Cwith woman
OL,7,F"He abused that position by
OL,8,Fdemonstrating predatory behaviour and
OL,9,Fpursuing an inappropriate
OL,10,Frelationship."
OL,12,FMr Campbell, added: "Female X was in a
OL,13,Fvulnerable position when she was
OL,14,Fmanipulated by DC Littlewood. He met
OL,15,Fher while on duty and used that
OL,16,Fcontact to start up a friendship which
OL,17,Fled to inappropriate contact including
OL,18,Fsexualised messages.
OL,26,@rD@NO]tD@UOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/7
