OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1776442271
OL,3,CPolice officer committed gross
OL,4,Cmisconduct for pursuing relationship
OL,5,Cwith woman
OL,7,F"The officer knew his behaviour was
OL,8,Fimproper as he told her to delete
OL,9,Fmessages, some of which were sent
OL,10,Fwhile on duty, as they would get him
OL,11,Finto trouble at work.
OL,13,F"Police professional standards are
OL,14,Fclear that officers should never use
OL,15,Ftheir position to establish or pursue
OL,16,Fimproper relationships with any
OL,17,Fvictims, witness, offenders or other
OL,18,Fvulnerable person and never enter into
OL,19,Finappropriate communication.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/7
