PN,37307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1776442271
OL,3,CPolice officer committed gross
OL,4,Cmisconduct for pursuing relationship
OL,5,Cwith woman
OL,7,F"Littlewood completed an integrity
OL,8,Fhealth check on 18 September 2023
OL,9,Fconfirming he understood the Code of
OL,10,FEthics and Professional Boundaries.
OL,11,FHowever. we found he exchanged
OL,12,Fhundreds of messages with her and it's
OL,13,Fclear he deleted many more."
